{
  "stem": "4967.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Or they used to take them to different forests and shoot them and bury them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And life became very difficult in the ghetto, particular when the German front got harder for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Food supplies in the ghetto barely came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Meat, we used to get once in two weeks, 100 grams horse meat brought from the front lines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Shot horses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Potatoes, very scarce.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Bread, very little and flour, very little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sugar and other amenities we never got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sickness became a disease in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "People used to get sick, and they used to be hospitalized wherever possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was-- the small ghetto had a hospital, and the big ghetto had a big hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one morning, I see they surrounded the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my place wasn't far from the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the connection between the-- the two ghettos was over a wooden bridge, like I saw a movie here in cinema, or whatever-- whatever was the name.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it reminded me of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they surrounded this little ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and I saw them taking out people, marching out of the ghetto towards the other side, to the-- to the forts.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all of a sudden, I hear an explosion and a big flame.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I see the Jewish hospital is burning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Afterwards, I find out that the Germans put in flammable material and detonated the hospital, and the doctors and the nurses and the assistants and the patients, everybody was blown up or burned alive.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this ghetto was liquidated in a matter of days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They took away everybody to the forts.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
